, and test all of the contacts and even isolate them,\" he stated. \"People may also keep stock of essentials if we say a week-long curfew will be imposed. We have recommended to take the step saying infection has increased a lot.\"\n\nThe Kathmandu Valley is under prohibitory orders since August 20 following a surge in COVID-19 infections. The one-week extension made last Wednesday will expire in the midnight.","title":"Mayors recommend week-long curfew in Kathmandu Valley","url":"http://en.setopati.com/social/153812","video":[]}
